//  Combined Game Console — Extended Edition
//  Target: Arduino Nano ESP32 (ESP32-S3)
//
//  MENU (9 items):
//    Games | Weather | SMS | Timer | NASA | Stocks | News | Calc | Settings
//
//  GAMES (8 total):
//    2048 | Tetris | Pong | Flappy Bird | Snake | Breakout | Minesweeper | Simon Says
//
//  FEATURES:
//    Weather + Air Quality Index (AQI via Open-Meteo, no key needed)
//    SMS via Twilio REST API
//    NASA Explorer: Planets | Moons | Artemis II | APOD
//    Stock Ticker: search any ticker, price + 5-day chart (Yahoo Finance)
//    News Headlines: BBC World RSS feed (no API key needed)
//    Calculator: full arithmetic with history line
//    Stopwatch with lap recording
//    Passive Buzzer: sound effects for games and alerts
//
//  BUZZER WIRING:
//    Buzzer + leg → Pin 7    Buzzer – leg → GND
//    (Comment out BUZZER_PIN if no buzzer is attached)
//
//  LIBRARIES (install via Arduino Library Manager):
//    Adafruit ST7789   Adafruit GFX
//    WiFi, HTTPClient, BLE, base64 are in the ESP32 Arduino core.
// ============================================================

